<L>__{interior willie's campaign office in hotel, day}
<A>__{the place is a beehive of activity, with typists and messengers scurrying about, all supervised by sadie.}
<C>__{sadie}
<D>__{hey, i need a boy... where's a boy?}
<P>__{(boy runs up)}
<D>__{take that downstairs; they're waiting for it. right away, on the double.}
<P>__{(to typist)}
<D>__{listen, baby, you've got to double space all of this... he can't read, see.}
